487
00:33:40,530 --> 00:33:42,640
<i>Though China has just begun,</i>

488
00:33:42,640 --> 00:33:45,850
<i>I believe that one day we will stand at the top of the world.</i>

489
00:33:45,850 --> 00:33:48,240
