497
00:34:12,580 --> 00:34:15,730
<i>Oh it's too cool!</i>

498
00:34:18,390 --> 00:34:21,150
<i>I don't want to look at him!</i>

499
00:34:21,150 --> 00:34:25,120
<i>Once you see it, if you still don't like it,</i>

500
00:34:25,120 --> 00:34:29,470
<i>I'll help you chase Han Shangyan back to Norway!</i>

501
00:34:30,620 --> 00:34:32,170
<i>Let's go.</i>

502
00:34:34,190 --> 00:34:40,750
After I came back, I slowly understand the birth of a championship is really not easy at all.

503
00:34:40,750 --> 00:34:43,730
