506
00:34:51,510 --> 00:34:55,580
Some people still don't really understand them.

507
00:34:55,580 --> 00:35:01,500
And Han Shangyan has never mentioned any of that bitterness.

508
00:35:01,500 --> 00:35:04,710
And suffered all that by himself.

509
00:35:04,710 --> 00:35:08,650
Of course these children have their flaws.

510
00:35:08,650 --> 00:35:13,490
But I think our child, Han Shangyan, is really a good kid.

511
00:35:14,480 --> 00:35:17,000
I remember at the time,

512
00:35:17,000 --> 00:35:22,870
